            <description><![CDATA[【⚠️转发提醒！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%85%A2%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BC%E7%97%9B%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E8%B6%8A%E5%BF%8D%E8%B6%8A%E7%97%9B%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%85%A2%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BC%E7%97%9B%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E8%B6%8A%E5%BF%8D%E8%B6%8A%E7%97%9B%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#慢性疼痛可能越忍越痛#</span></a>】“慢性疼痛”指持续时间大于3个月的疼痛，如头痛、三叉神经痛等。有报告统计，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E8%B6%853%E4%BA%BF%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%AD%E5%8F%97%E6%85%A2%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BC%E7%97%9B%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E8%B6%853%E4%BA%BF%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%AD%E5%8F%97%E6%85%A2%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BC%E7%97%9B%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#我国超3亿人遭受慢性疼痛#</span></a>，疼痛已成为心脑血管疾病、肿瘤之后的第三大健康问题。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>医生提醒，慢性疼痛病因复杂，往往时间越长治疗越复杂，且可能越忍越痛，需早就诊、早治疗👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4957586496356376" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hixg2in25vj61x112ub2902.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/SQsthUOMlx089quU6Daw01041201mkPs0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1697534218&amp;ssig=%2F2X8ilqZJ6&amp;KID=unisto